s\": 106.99,\n      \"num_decode_reqs\": 8.014\n    }\n  },\n  \"step_overhead_us\": 3896.76,\n  \"output_token_processing_time_us\": 0,\n  \"scheduling_processing_time_us\": 0,\n  \"preemption_processing_time_us\": 0\n}\n```\n\n#### Version 2 (regime-switching, \"step_time_regimes\" key)\n\nFound across both ideas. These contain a `\"step_time_regimes\"` array with conditional regime selection and per-regime linear models.\n\n**Idea 1 (Bayesian Calibration) -- 2-regime piecewise artifacts (23 files):**\n\nLocated in three directories:\n- `idea-1-bayesian-calibration/h1-piecewise-steptime/output/artifacts/` (5 base artifacts, `_piecewise.json`)\n- `idea-1-bayesian-calibration/h4-model-generalization/output/lomo_artifacts/` (5 LOMO artifacts)\n- `idea-1-bayesian-calibration/h5-workload-generalization/output/lowo_artifacts/` (13 LOWO artifacts)\n\nExample (llama-2-7b_tp1_piecewise.json): Two regimes -- `decode_only` (prefill_tokens == 0) and `mixed_batch` (fallback). Features: prefill_tokens, decode_tokens, prefill_x_decode.\n\n**Idea 2 (Regime Ensemble) -- 3-regime artifacts (49 files):**\n\nLocated in five directories:\n- `idea-2-regime-ensemble/h1-kv-regime-models/output/artifacts/` (10 files: 5 `_regime.json` + 5 `_single.json`)\n- `idea-2-regime-ensemble/h3-secondary-method-calibration/output/calibrated_artifacts/` (5 calibrated `_regime.json`)\n- `idea-2-regime-ensemble/h4-model-generalization/output/lomo_artifacts/` (5 LOMO `_regime.json`)\n- `idea-2-regime-ensemble/h5-workload-generalization/output/lowo_artifacts/` (18 LOWO `_regime.json`, per model x workload)\n- `idea-2-regime-ensemble/h2-blis-e2e-validation/output/e2e_summary_regime.json` (1 summary)\n\nExample structure (llama-2-7b_tp1_regime.json, H1 base artifact):\n```json\n{\n  \"version\": 2,\n  \"step_time_regimes\": [\n    {\n      \"name\": \"decode_only\",\n      \"condition\": {\"feature\": \"prefill_tokens\", \"op\": \"==\", \"value\": 0},\n      \"model\": {\n        \"model_type\": \"linear\",\n        \"intercept\": -37.37,\n        \"feature_coefficients\": {\n          \"decode_tokens\": 7.95,\n          \"num_decode_reqs\": 7.95\n        }\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"mixed_light\",\n      \"condition\": {\"feature\": \"prefill_tokens\", \"op\": \"<\", \"value\": 256},\n      \"model\": {\n        \"model_type\": \"linear\",\n        \"intercept\": -77.98,\n        \"feature_coefficients\": {\n          \"prefill_tokens\": 28.71, \"decode_tokens\": 8.24,\n          \"num_prefill_reqs\": 48.63, \"num_decode_reqs\": 8.24,\n          \"prefill_x_decode\": -0.16, \"prefill_sq\": -0.81\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"step_overhead_us\": 3896.76,\n  \"output_token_processing_time_us\": 0,\n  \"scheduling_processing_time_us\": 0,\n  \"preemption_processing_time_us\": 0\n}\n```\n\nThe **calibrated** H3 artifacts additionally include `scheduling_processing_time_us` and a `queueing_time` object (e.g., 202us for llama-2-7b).\n\nThe **LOMO** H4 artifacts include 3 regimes (decode_only, mixed_light, mixed_heavy with null condition as fallback) and KV features (kv_sum, kv_max, kv_mean, kv_std, decode_x_kv_mean).\n\nThe **E2E summary** (`e2e_summary_regime.json`):\n```json\n{\n  \"mode\": \"regime\",\n  \"n_completed\": 10,\n  \"n_skipped\": 0,\n  \"mean_e2e_error_pct\": 427.81,\n  \"mean_ttft_error_pct\": 31905.77,\n  \"mean_itl_error_pct\": 33.64,\n  \"experiments_below_10pct\": 1\n}\n```\n\n**Models covered across all artifacts:** llama-2-7b (TP1), codellama-34b (TP2), llama-2-70b (TP4), llama-2-70b-hf (TP4), mixtral-8x7b-v0-1 (TP2).\n\n---\n\n### 2. Directories Named \"round2\" or Containing \"idea-2\"\n\nSix directories found:\n\n| Directory | Description |\n|---|---|\n| `/Users/dipanwitaguhathakurta/Downloads/inference-sim-package/BLIS-research/hypotheses/h-stepml/round2/` | Main Round 2 research directory (BLIS-research repo) |\n| `/Users/dipanwitaguhathakurta/Downloads/inference-sim-package/BLIS-research/hypotheses/h-stepml/round2/idea-2