{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_0174kr8bM4mFmu87uFzpnpWe","type":"tool_result","content":"{\n  \"version\": 2,\n  \"step_time_regimes\": [\n    {\n      \"name\": \"decode_only\",\n      \"condition\": {\n        \"feature\": \"prefill_tokens\",\n        \"op\": \"==\",\n        \"value\": 0\n      },\n      \"model\": {\n        \"model_type\": \"linear\",\n        \"intercept\": -37.37132221350058,\n        \"feature_coefficients\": {\n          \"decode_tokens\": 7.951495295146752,\n          \"num_decode_reqs\": 7.951495295147041\n        }\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"mixed_light\",\n      \"condition\": {\n        \"feature\": \"prefill_tokens\",\n        \"op\": \"<\",\n        \"value\": 256\n      },\n      \"model\": {\n        \"model_type\": \"linear\",\n        \"intercept\": -77.97943712885353,\n        \"feature_coefficients\": {\n          \"prefill_tokens\": 28.707846070521985,\n          \"decode_tokens\": 8.238725686646465,\n          \"num_prefill_reqs\": 48.63455190521838,\n          \"num_decode_reqs\": 8.238725687421233,\n          \"prefill_x_decode\": -0.15969273704853537,\n          \"prefill_sq\": -0.8113619055257316\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"step_overhead_us\": 3896.7631749593834,\n  \"output_token_processing_time_us\": 0,\n  \"scheduling_processing_time_us\": 202.036,\n  \"preemption_processing_time_us\": 0,\n  \"queueing_time\": {\n    \"model_type\": \"linear\",\n    \"intercept\": 202.036,\n    \"feature_coefficients\": {}\n  }\n}","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"7ea608f4-4aa5-4264-9119-cf38f8fb2f5c","uuid":"eec24183-da1d-44ba-b218-41c1cca66033","tool_use_result":{"stdout":"{\n  \"version\": 2,\n  \"step_time_regimes\": [\n    {\n      \"name\": \"decode_only\",\n      \"condition\": {\n        \"feature\": \"prefill_tokens\",\n        \"op\": \"==\",\n        \"value\": 0\n      },\n      \"model\": {\n        \"model_type\": \"linear\",\n        \"intercept\": -37.37132221350058,\n        \"feature_coefficients\": {\n          \"decode_tokens\": 7.951495295146752,\n          \"num_decode_reqs\": 7.951495295147041\n        }\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"mixed_light\",\n      \"condition\": {\n        \"feature\": \"prefill_tokens\",\n        \"op\": \"<\",\n        \"value\": 256\n      },\n      \"model\": {\n        \"model_type\": \"linear\",\n        \"intercept\": -77.97943712885353,\n        \"feature_coefficients\": {\n          \"prefill_tokens\": 28.707846070521985,\n          \"decode_tokens\": 8.238725686646465,\n          \"num_prefill_reqs\": 48.63455190521838,\n          \"num_decode_reqs\": 8.238725687421233,\n          \"prefill_x_decode\": -0.15969273704853537,\n          \"prefill_sq\": -0.8113619055257316\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"step_overhead_us\": 3896.7631749593834,\n  \"output_token_processing_time_us\": 0,\n  \"scheduling_processing_time_us\": 202.036,\n  \"preemption_processing_time_us\": 0,\n  \"queueing_time\": {\n    \"model_type\": \"linear\",\n    \"intercept\": 202.036,\n    \"feature_coefficients\": {}\n  }\n}","stderr":"","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false}}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"msg_bdrk_012CVx9BG7EmcVRr7dK4S3CH","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"claude-opus-4-6","content":[{"type":"text","text":"`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`\nThe calibrated artifacts use a **regime ensemble** with 2-3 regimes (decode-only, mixed-light, mixed-heavy) differentiated by `prefill_tokens`. The `step_overhead_us` (~3.9ms) acts as a floor for minimum step cycle time, modeling the CPU overhead that dominates small batches. The `scheduling_processing_time_us` (202µs) was calibrated in Round 2's H3 to account for vLLM's scheduler overhead per batch formation cycle.\n`─────────────────────────────────────────────────`\n\nNow let me create the experiment. I need to:\n1. Build the BLIS binary\n2. Convert lifecycle data to CSV traces \n3. Run BLIS with trace replay for each experiment\n4. Compare against workload-spec results"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"output_tokens":0},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"7ea608f4-4aa5-4264-9119-cf38f8fb2f5c","uuid":"f4cc4d33-0103-4ae2-9d4a-11ed804f967f"}
